Harry Beresford https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harry_Beresford 0 Harry J. Beresford (November 4, 1863 – October 4, 1944) was an English-born actor on the American stage and in motion pictures. He used the professional name Harry J. Morgan early in his career. Harry_J._Beresford ( November_4_,_1863 – October_4_,_1944 ) was an_English-born_actor on the_American_stage and in motion_pictures .
